00:00:27.273 --> 00:00:32.943
Elements, sometimes called Rare Earth Metals, or just ‘Rare Earths’ for short.

00:00:33.913 --> 00:00:38.373
These are the 17 chemical elements that are very important for a

00:00:38.383 --> 00:00:43.133
lot of the technology that you and I probably use on a daily basis.

00:00:43.703 --> 00:00:48.893
From laptops to mobile phones, electric cars to aeroplanes,

00:00:48.913 --> 00:00:53.283
missiles to magnets, Rare Earths are almost everywhere.

